Analysis of the Main Target Image:

• There are essentially two separate sub‐structures:

  1) LEFT “TOWER”‐LIKE STRUCTURE  
     – Total of four vertical “layers”:  
       Layer 1 (Bottom): One wide yellow rectangular plank.  
       Layer 2: Two orange cylinders standing on top of that yellow plank.  
       Layer 3: Another wide yellow rectangular plank resting atop the two cylinders.  
       Layer 4 (Top “House”):  
         • A red rectangular block standing vertically in the middle,  
         • Flanked on each side by a vertical blue rectangular block,  
         • Topped by two orange triangular wedges forming a peaked roof.  

  2) RIGHT “WINDOW”‐LIKE STRUCTURE  
     – Built in three horizontal layers:  
       Layer 1 (Bottom): One wide yellow rectangular plank.  
       Layer 2 (Middle):  
         • One red arch block in the center (the circular opening faces front),  
         • A tall green rectangular block on both the left and right sides,  
       Layer 3 (Top): Another wide yellow rectangular plank.  

Required Blocks from the Dictionary (with exact orientations as shown):

• Index 1 (Red arch), used 1 ×  
• Index 5 (Red rectangular block), used 1 ×  
• Index 7 (Blue rectangular block, vertical), used 2 ×  
• Index 8 (Green rectangular block, vertical), used 2 ×  
• Index 9 (Yellow rectangular plank, horizontal), used 4 ×  
• Index 11 (Orange cylinder), used 2 ×  
• Index 13 (Orange wedge), used 1 ×  
• Index 14 (Orange wedge), used 1 ×  

Step‐by‐Step Assembly Instructions:

{
  Step1: Move block with index 9      // Bottom yellow plank of the left tower
  Step2: Move block with index 11     // First orange cylinder on left tower
  Step3: Move block with index 11     // Second orange cylinder on left tower
  Step4: Move block with index 9      // Top yellow plank over the two cylinders
  Step5: Move block with index 5      // Red rectangular block (center of “house”)
  Step6: Move block with index 7      // Blue vertical block (left side of red block)
  Step7: Move block with index 7      // Blue vertical block (right side of red block)
  Step8: Move block with index 13     // First orange wedge (left half of roof)
  Step9: Move block with index 14     // Second orange wedge (right half of roof)

  Step10: Move block with index 9     // Bottom yellow plank of the right “window”
  Step11: Move block with index 8     // Green vertical block on left side
  Step12: Move block with index 8     // Green vertical block on right side
  Step13: Move block with index 1     // Red arch (circular opening faces front)
  Step14: Move block with index 9     // Top yellow plank of the right structure
}
